有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻 综合报道2月16日，武汉。
A surging news report on Feb. 16, Wuhan.
在法律政策允许下，两例新冠逝者遗体解剖工作在金银潭医院完成，由解剖获得的新冠肺炎病理，目前已被送检。
With the permission of the law and policy, the autopsy of the bodies of the deceased in the new crown was completed at the Gold and Silver Pool Hospital and the new crown pneumonia obtained by autopsy has now been submitted for examination.
Play澎湃新闻记者 祝文博 编辑 张兆亿 视频来源 相关人士责任编辑：周宽玮据参与解剖工作的法医病理学专家、湖北省司法鉴定协会会长刘良介绍，他和团队成员及相关专家共同对两例逝者遗体进行解剖，每例耗时近3个小时，解剖病理已经送检，预计10天以内可以得出结论。
Zhang Weiwei, a forensic pathologist involved in the autopsy and head of the Hubei Provincial Judicial Accreditation Association, said Zhou Kuan Weiwei, a forensic pathologist involved in the autopsy, and Liu Liang, head of the Hubei Provincial Judicial Accreditation Association, conducted autopsies on the bodies of two deceased patients, each taking nearly three hours.
2月16日23时12分，刘良在个人头条账号“法医刘良”上发文详述18小时内连续尸检2例新冠肺炎遗体的经过——2月15日21时许，刘良突然接到金银潭医院院长张定宇电话，称有一个新冠肺炎逝世患者遗体可以做解剖手术。
At 23: 12 p.m. on Feb. 16, Liu Liang posted a letter detailing two consecutive autopsies of two new cases of pneumonia within 18 hours - Liu Liang received a telephone call from Zhang Dingyu, the director of the Gold and Silver Pool Hospital, on February 15.
刘良紧急安排团队成员汇集至金银潭医院，等至凌晨1点多开始尸检。
Mr Lau arranged for the team members to assemble at the Gold and Silver Pool Hospital and wait until 1: 00 a.m. for the autopsy.
图为刘良（左）身着防护服首次穿防护服，不到10分钟，刘良就满头大汗，呼吸困难，眼镜护目镜朦胧一片。
Liu Liang (left), wearing protective clothing for the first time, less than 10 minutes, Liu Liang sweaty, breathing difficulties, glasses hazy one.
手术做到大半截，他出现低血糖症状，心慌头晕。
Most of the surgery was performed, and he developed hypoglycemia and dizziness.
3时50分，尸检结束。
At 0350 hours, the autopsy was completed.
回家睡了2小时，刘良醒来和团队成员总结尸检流程上可以改善和提高的地方以及后勤保障问题，并将相关情况反馈给相关负责人。
After two hours' sleep, Liu woke up and the team members summed up the improvements and improvements in the autopsy procedures and logistical problems, and reported back to the relevant officials.
图为刘良（中）和团队成员合影2月16日11时许，刘良再次接到张定宇电话，又有一例新冠肺炎患者遗体要进行尸检。
Photo shows Liu Liang (middle) and team members. At about 11: 00 pm on February 16, Liu Dingyu received another call from Zhang Dingyu.
刘良再次紧急召集人员，前往金银潭医院，下午16时许尸检，18时30分结束。
Liu Liang again called in an emergency to go to the Gold and Silver Pool Hospital for an autopsy at about 16: 00 p.m. and ended at 18: 30 p.m.
刘良认为，这次尸检得以这么快进行，得益于家属的同意，同时也得益于国家卫健委高效的紧急会议，基本上是特事特办的模式，在紧急出台文件的同时，迅速给重点医院口头通知。
Liu said the autopsy was carried out so quickly, thanks to the family's consent and an efficient emergency meeting of the State Council for Health, basically a special-purpose model that quickly gives oral notification to key hospitals while documents are being produced on an urgent basis.
2月15日，国家卫生健康委员会医政医管局在武汉召开会议研究新冠肺炎病死病例尸检有关事宜，并邀请刘良作为参会专家。
On February 15, the National Health Council's Medical and Health Administration held a meeting in Wuhan to study the autopsy of the death cases of Newcastle pneumonia and invited Liu Liang as an expert.
刘良透露，2月16日尸检前，他们专门为逝者默哀。
Before the autopsy on February 16, they observed a moment of silence for the dead, Liu said.
据了解，由解剖获得的新冠肺炎病理已送检，有望寻找到新冠肺炎的致病性、致死性病理，给未来临床治疗危重症患者提供依据。
It is understood that the new crown pneumonia pathology obtained from the autopsy has been sent for examination, hopefully to find the pathogenicity, fatal pathology of the new crown pneumonia, to provide the basis for future clinical treatment of critically ill patients.
